'''Gary''' gave Richard and Adele Webber a tour of [[Roseridge Home for Extended Care]].

==History==
When Richard and Adele started to look into residential care for Adele, they went to Roseridge. Gary gave them a tour and gave them information about the care she would receive there.

==Career==
Gary works at [[Roseridge Home for Extended Care]]. When [[Richard Webber|Richard]] and [[Adele Webber]] were considering Roseridge for Adele's care, he gave them a tour.
